            <h2><a name="TOC-Six-aspects-of-project-performance-to-be-managed"></a>Six aspects of project performance to be managed</h2>
            <div>
              <ul><li>Costs</li>
                <li>Timescales</li>
                <li>Quality</li>
                <li>Scope</li>
                <li>Risk</li>
                <li>Benefits</li></ul>
              Managing the above requires <b>planning</b>, <b>delegation</b>, <b>monitoring</b> and <b>control</b>.
            </div>
