          <h2><a name="TOC-Definition-and-five-characteristics-of-a-project"></a>Definition and five characteristics of a project</h2>
          <div>
            <div class="sites-codeblock sites-codesnippet-block"><code>A project is a temporary organisation that is created for the purpose of delivering one or more business products according to an agreed Business Case.</code></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <ul><li>Change</li>
              <li>Temporary</li>
              <li>Cross-functional</li>
              <li>Unique</li>
              <li>Uncertainty</li></ul>
          </div>
